http.title: Dog Walking Montrose Pet Sitting Montrose My Happy Paws
http.html:
Welcome to My Happy Paws

Your local family run Dog Walking,Pet Sitting and Home Visit  Service covering St Cyrus, Montrose, Johnshaven and surrounding areas.

At My Happy Paws we aim to provide a friendly, safe, reliable and professional service taylored to each individual customers needs. You can be safe in the knowledge that your pets will be well cared for at all times and given as much attention as if they were part of the family as well.

My Happy Paws is fully insured for public liability, including care and custodial and key cover. We are also police checked and verified, and currently hold an up to date Canine First Aid Certificate.

Want a Quote?

Visit the Contact page with details of your requirements. 

(Copies of any of the above documents can be made available on request)
